Branchiostegal membranes broadly attached to isthmus; gill openings extend anteroventrally to a vertical approximately one eye lens behind orbit. Gill rakers tubercular, none on outer side of first gill arch; outer gill slit greatly restricted, its vertical opening greater than barbel length (slightly longer in one 
